author: Eleanor Roosevelt
message: Friendship with oneself is all important because without it one cannot be friends with anybody else in the world.
title: Thought of the day

author: Robert Fulghum
message: Peace is not something you wish for. It's something you make, something you do, something you are, and something you give away.
title: Thought of the day

author: Bruce Lee
message: A wise man can learn more from a foolish question than a fool can learn from a wise answer.
title: Thought of the day

author: Arthur Schopenhauer
message: Every man takes the limits of his own field of vision for the limits of the world.
title: Thought of the day
